    <hangnum nr="790"/>
    <gatha type="1"> ‘‘Kāme ādittato disvā, jātarūpāni satthato;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Gabbhavokkantito dukkhaṃ, nirayesu mahabbhayaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="791"/>
    <gatha type="1"> ‘‘Etamādīnavaṃ ñatvā, saṃvegaṃ alabhiṃ tadā;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Sohaṃ viddho tadā santo, sampatto āsavakkhayaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="792"/>
    <gatha type="1"> ‘‘Pariciṇṇo mayā satthā, kataṃ buddhassa sāsanaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Ohito garuko bhāro, bhavanetti samūhatā.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="793"/>
    <gatha type="1"> ‘‘Yassatthāya pabbajito, agārasmānagāriyaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">So me attho anuppatto, sabbasaṃyojanakkhayo’’ti.</gatha>
    <centered>… Raṭṭhapālo thero….</centered>
